{"title":"Cannondale confirmed for Cyclist Track Days plus Easter flash sale: Save £10 on tickets!","link":"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-2023","date":1680706800000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-2023\">Cannondale confirmed for Cyclist Track Days plus Easter flash sale: Save £10 on tickets!</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://cyclisttrackdays.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Cyclist Track Days</a> are back for 2023 with two events on the calendar: one at <strong><a href=\"https://www.visitleevalley.org.uk/lee-valley-velopark\" target=\"_blank\">Lee Valley VeloPark</a> on the 15th and 16th of April</strong>, and one at <strong>Castle Combe Race Circuit in Wiltshire on June 4</strong>.  </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>For a limited time only, tickets to both events are available at a discount of £10 off. To claim this, simply enter promo code EASTER at the checkout. This sale runs until 10th April 2023 at midnight.</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Track Days offer a unique opportunity to get some proper saddle time on some incredible road and gravel bikes, and they’re held on closed circuits so you can concentrate on getting to know them without worrying about traffic.  </p>\n\n\n\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"https://cyclisttrackdays.com/trackdays/en/page/tickets#book-now\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Book your Cyclist Track Day Tickets now</strong></a></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<p>Full Track Tickets for the events cost just £30 (from £20 for Cyclist subscribers!), which includes:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Unlimited riding time </li><li>A coffee, plus lunch and dessert provided by The Calzone Kitchen</li><li>The chance to meet like-minded cyclists <em>and </em>members of the <em>Cyclist</em> editorial team</li><li>A <em>Cyclist </em>goody bag</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Groups of four or more get an automatic 15% discount on Track Tickets while non-riders who want to come along have the option of a £10 spectator ticket that includes track-side access and a coffee. </p>\n\n\n\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"https://cyclisttrackdays.com/trackdays/en/page/tickets#book-now\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Book your Cyclist Track Day Tickets now</strong></a></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<p>The full list of bike makers and models available to ride will be finalised closer to the event dates, but the brands below are confirmed. Here’s a selection of the bikes you can expect to try out: </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>3T  </h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"747\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/01/3TleadOut-970x747.jpg\" alt=\"3T Strada ICR\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/01/3TleadOut-970x747.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/01/3TleadOut-300x231.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/01/3TleadOut-768x591.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/01/3TleadOut-1536x1183.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/01/3TleadOut-750x578.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/01/3TleadOut-1140x878.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/01/3TleadOut.jpg 2000w\" /><figcaption>Tapestry</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The latest <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/3t-strada-icr\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>3T Strada</strong></a> features ultra-clean cable routing and a gorgeous aero frameset. Expect to see a selection of gravel bikes too including the <strong><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/3t-exploro-ultra-2022\" target=\"_blank\">Exploro Ultra</a>, Exploro Boost</strong>, <strong>Exploro Team</strong> and <strong><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/3t-exploro-racemax-first-ride-review\" target=\"_blank\">Exploro RaceMax</a></strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>BMC  </h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/bmc-teammachine-slr-01-four-arctic-silver-prisma-carbon-1_2-1-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"Road bike\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/bmc-teammachine-slr-01-four-arctic-silver-prisma-carbon-1_2-1-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/bmc-teammachine-slr-01-four-arctic-silver-prisma-carbon-1_2-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/bmc-teammachine-slr-01-four-arctic-silver-prisma-carbon-1_2-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/bmc-teammachine-slr-01-four-arctic-silver-prisma-carbon-1_2-1-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/bmc-teammachine-slr-01-four-arctic-silver-prisma-carbon-1_2-1-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/bmc-teammachine-slr-01-four-arctic-silver-prisma-carbon-1_2-1-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/bmc-teammachine-slr-01-four-arctic-silver-prisma-carbon-1_2-1-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/bmc-teammachine-slr-01-four-arctic-silver-prisma-carbon-1_2-1-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/bmc-teammachine-slr-01-four-arctic-silver-prisma-carbon-1_2-1-350x233.jpg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/bmc-teammachine-slr-01-four-arctic-silver-prisma-carbon-1_2-1.jpg 1920w\" /><figcaption>BMC</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/bmc-teammachine-slr01-one-review\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Teammachine SLR 01</strong></a> is a stunning race bike with WorldTour pedigree.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Cannondale</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"577\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/03/Cannondale-SuperSix-carbon-1-970x577.jpg\" alt=\"Road bike\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/03/Cannondale-SuperSix-carbon-1-970x577.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/03/Cannondale-SuperSix-carbon-1-300x178.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/03/Cannondale-SuperSix-carbon-1-768x457.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/03/Cannondale-SuperSix-carbon-1-750x446.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/03/Cannondale-SuperSix-carbon-1-1140x678.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/03/Cannondale-SuperSix-carbon-1.jpg 1535w\" /><figcaption>Cannondale</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The brand new <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/cannondale-supersix-evo-review\" target=\"_blank\">Cannondale SuperSix Evo</a> is a proper flagship race bike that’s only just launched. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Canyon </h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"546\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/full_2023_ultimate-cf-slx-8-etap_3321_P02_P5-970x546.jpg\" alt=\"Road bike\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/full_2023_ultimate-cf-slx-8-etap_3321_P02_P5-970x546.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/full_2023_ultimate-cf-slx-8-etap_3321_P02_P5-300x169.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/full_2023_ultimate-cf-slx-8-etap_3321_P02_P5-768x432.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/full_2023_ultimate-cf-slx-8-etap_3321_P02_P5-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/full_2023_ultimate-cf-slx-8-etap_3321_P02_P5-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/full_2023_ultimate-cf-slx-8-etap_3321_P02_P5-750x422.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/full_2023_ultimate-cf-slx-8-etap_3321_P02_P5-1140x641.jpg 1140w\" /><figcaption>Canyon</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The <strong><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/canyon-ultimate-review\" target=\"_blank\">Canyon Ultimate CF SLX 8 eTap</a></strong> is a full bells-and-whistles lightweight road bike. The slippery <strong><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/canyon-aeroad-cfr-first-ride-review-canyon-s-fastest-bike-ever\" target=\"_blank\">Aeroad CF SLX 8 Di2</a></strong> and the distance-focussed <strong><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/canyon-endurace-cf-7-etap-review\" target=\"_blank\">Endurace CF SL7 eTap</a></strong> will also feature. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Factor (London event only) </h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Factor_OSTRO_FRG_DA_180-DriveSide-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"Road bike\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Factor_OSTRO_FRG_DA_180-DriveSide-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Factor_OSTRO_FRG_DA_180-DriveSide-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Factor_OSTRO_FRG_DA_180-DriveSide-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Factor_OSTRO_FRG_DA_180-DriveSide-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Factor_OSTRO_FRG_DA_180-DriveSide-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Factor_OSTRO_FRG_DA_180-DriveSide-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Factor_OSTRO_FRG_DA_180-DriveSide-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Factor_OSTRO_FRG_DA_180-DriveSide-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Factor_OSTRO_FRG_DA_180-DriveSide-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Factor_OSTRO_FRG_DA_180-DriveSide-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Factor</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The <strong><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/factor-ostro-vam-review\" target=\"_blank\">Factor Ostro VAM</a></strong>, as raced by one Chris Froome. Seriously rapid. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Orro </h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Orro-Venturi-STC-Black-Stealth-Rival-Etap-Edit-large-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"Road bike\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Orro-Venturi-STC-Black-Stealth-Rival-Etap-Edit-large-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Orro-Venturi-STC-Black-Stealth-Rival-Etap-Edit-large-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Orro-Venturi-STC-Black-Stealth-Rival-Etap-Edit-large-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Orro-Venturi-STC-Black-Stealth-Rival-Etap-Edit-large-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Orro-Venturi-STC-Black-Stealth-Rival-Etap-Edit-large-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Orro-Venturi-STC-Black-Stealth-Rival-Etap-Edit-large-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Orro-Venturi-STC-Black-Stealth-Rival-Etap-Edit-large-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Orro-Venturi-STC-Black-Stealth-Rival-Etap-Edit-large-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Orro-Venturi-STC-Black-Stealth-Rival-Etap-Edit-large-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Orro-Venturi-STC-Black-Stealth-Rival-Etap-Edit-large-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Orro</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Precise models are TBC, but the <strong>Orro Venturi STC</strong>, <strong>Gold STC</strong> and <strong>Terra</strong> will all be in attendance. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Ribble  </h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Ribble-Ultra-SL-R-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"Road bike\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Ribble-Ultra-SL-R-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Ribble-Ultra-SL-R-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Ribble-Ultra-SL-R-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Ribble-Ultra-SL-R-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Ribble-Ultra-SL-R-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Ribble-Ultra-SL-R-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Ribble-Ultra-SL-R-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Ribble-Ultra-SL-R-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Ribble-Ultra-SL-R-350x233.jpg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/02/Ribble-Ultra-SL-R.jpg 1600w\" /><figcaption>Ribble</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Ribble’s space age-looking <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/ribble-ultra-road-launch-all-new-aero-bike-with-unique-bars\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Ultra SLR</strong></a> will be on hand to slice through some wind, along with the <strong>Gravel SL</strong> and <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/ribble-cgr-ti-sport-review\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>CGR Ti</strong></a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"https://cyclisttrackdays.com/trackdays/en/page/tickets#book-now\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Book your Cyclist Track Day Tickets now</strong></a></div>\n</div>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-2023\">Cannondale confirmed for Cyclist Track Days plus Easter flash sale: Save £10 on tickets!</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a>.</p>","author":"Matthew Loveridge &#124; Website Editor","siteTitle":"Cyclist.co.uk","siteHash":"561486e7070fa5351de9318ad0fa26c2a39332acba5fc7c7d1694a01d53d431e","entryHash":"9f28926e32d470627056f682268b8834aa2ed570d360bc8a2eb8808f40437986","category":"Cycling"}